### ğŸ¨ Design Style Guidelines

**Primary colors:**
- ğŸŸª Primary: `#6C4AB6` (royal purple â€“ premium, calm)
- ğŸ¾ Accent: `#FF9F1C` (warm amber â€“ emotional, fun)
- âšª Background: `#FAFAFA` (light grey/white)
